Ants from El Hierro have not received any special attention and only nine species have been noted:
Crematogaster alluaudi Crematogaster alluaudi (Wellenius, 1955: Frontera);
Temnothorax gracilicornis nivarianus Temnothorax gracilicornis nivarianus (Wellenius, 1955: Frontera);
Tetramorium semilaeve depressum Tetramorium semilaeve depressum (Wellenius, 1955: Guarazoca, El Pinar, Frontera);
Cardiocondyla mauritanica Cardiocondyla mauritanica Forel (Seifert, 2003: without locality);
Linepithema humile Linepithema humile (Wellenius, 1955: Valverde);
Plagiolepis barbara canariensis Plagiolepis barbara canariensis (Wellenius, 1955: Guarazoca, El Brezal, Frontera);
Camponotus hesperius Camponotus hesperius (Wellenius, 1955: Valverde, Guarazoca, El Pinar, El

Brezal, Frontera);
Camponotus feai Camponotus feai (Wellenius, 1955: Valverde; Barquin, 1981: La Lajura, La Restinga);
Camponotus guanchus Camponotus guanchus (Wellenius, 1955: Guarazoca, Frontera; Cagniant & Espadaler, 1993: El Sabinal).
